  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for perplexing prisms and parabolic puzzles in BEAM BOUND! Solve increasingly complex laser-based stages within a Machiavellian mirrored maze. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/8844b944d8ab56a92ad9f9ad7e05d18a.poster.avif?t=1741616521\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/8844b944d8ab56a92ad9f9ad7e05d18a.webm?t=1741616521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/8844b944d8ab56a92ad9f9ad7e05d18a.mp4?t=1741616521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CREATE YOUR OWN LEVELS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the built-in Level Editor to create and upload your maps to the Steam Workshop or download and play Community made ones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/db0495e6ccdb9182d721943a9cf75446.poster.avif?t=1741616521\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/db0495e6ccdb9182d721943a9cf75446.webm?t=1741616521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560480/extras/db0495e6ccdb9182d721943a9cf75446.mp4?t=1741616521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
